dct_description_sm: Published at Washington D.C. March, 1901, reissued; January 1904 by th U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey O. H. Tittmann, Superintendent.
Depths shown by soundings and lines; relief at (at mountain peaks) by hachures and spot heights.
Lights and tides tables, storm warning displays, signs and abbreviations table (for wrecks, rocks, seabed makeup).
